Class Manager

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.nwillc.funjdbc.migrate.Manager
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DbAccessor, ConnectionProvider

    public class Manager
extends java.lang.Object
implements DbAccessor
    The migration Manager. This singleton manages a set of Migrations, performing them as needed and persisting the status of each.
